          "antonyms": [],
          "example": "to plump oysters or scallops by placing them in fresh or brackish water"
        },
        {
          "definition": "To cast or let drop all at once, suddenly and heavily.",
          "synonyms": [],
          "antonyms": [],
          "example": "to plump a stone into water"
        },
        {
